https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/NovaTwinsMOBOAwards-performers-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/NovaTwinsMOBOAwards-performers-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> MOBO奖宣布了2025年仪式的表演者更多。查找下面的所有详细信息。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mobo-founder-kanya-king-interview-alternative-dance-jamal-edwards-3358329"><b>MOBO创始人Kanya King在奖项的新类型中 - “这感觉就像是正确的一年”</b></a></strong></li></ul><p>庆祝《黑人原产》音乐的第27届年度活动<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-mobos-heading-to-newcastle-first-time-2025-3799241">将于2月18日星期二首次在纽卡斯尔举行</a>，该活动将于2月18日星期二举行。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jorja-smith">Jorja</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jorja-smith">Smith</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sampha">Sampha</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bashy">Bashy</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ghetts">Ghetts</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cleo-sol">Cleo Sol</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/central-cee">Central Cee</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/odeal">Odeal</a> Lead今年的提名获得了三个点头。<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mobo-awards-2025-see-the-full-list-of-nominees-3818607">在此处查看完整列表</a>。</p><div class="td-a-ad id_inline_ad0 id_ad_content-horiz-center"><p>上个月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/spice-krept-konan-and-bashy-announced-as-mobo-2025-performers-3830321">组织者确认Spice，Krept＆Konan和Bashy都将在当晚进行现场表演</a>。现在，已经揭示了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nova-twins">Nova Twins</a>和Odeal之类的人也将登上舞台。</p></div><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/darkoo">Darkoo</a> ，DJ AG， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pozer">Pozer</a>和Leostaytrill加入了他们的阵容。</p><p>此外，Mobos 2025将通过一个阶段的类型中汇集“一些最强大的声音”来庆祝英国R＆B。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DFuWfSwsFJS/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-i